out and said that, but,

222
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:44,123
he did ask him his opinion
about a girl last week.

223
00:18:44,166 --> 00:18:46,386
- I'm not saying it has
anything to with Brian, but

224
00:18:46,429 --> 00:18:49,128
